id: 062
title: "Big-run Guard (Confirmation Required)"
description: |
  Any pipeline execution that reads > BIGRUN_THRESHOLD_NOUNS nouns MUST require confirmation.
  Use the guard script and set CONFIRM_BIGRUN=YES to proceed; otherwise, refuse the edit/run.
alwaysApply: true
files:
  - "scripts/guards/guard_big_run.py"
notes:
  - "Environment: BIGRUN_THRESHOLD_NOUNS (default 2000), CONFIRM_BIGRUN=YES to override."